high_descs: Turn right, proceed to counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up knife closest to edge of counter, to the right of the green sponge.
Turn around, proceed half way down counter on right.  Turn right to face counter with bread on it.
Slice bread on counter with knife.
Place knife on top of bread.
Remove center slice of bread.
Turn around, proceed to counter, turn left and proceed to stove.
Open microwave above stove, put slice of bread in microwave behind the egg, shut microwave door.  Wait four seconds, open microwave door, remove bread slice, close door.
Turn left, proceed to counter to right.  Turn right to face counter.
Put bread on counter, standing on its bottom, to the right of the green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Slice bread, warm it in microwave, put on counter.

high_descs: Turn right and move to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife closest to you.
Turn around and move to the counter top on the left of the fridge.
Slice the loaf of bread.
Set the knife on its blade leaning against the loaf of bread.
Pick up a piece of bread from the middle of the loaf.
Turn around and move to the stove and microwave cross the room on your left.
Cook the bread in the microwave behind the egg for a few seconds and then take  then remove the bread.
Move back to the counter top to the left of the stove.
Set the slice of bread on the counter in front of the knife and to the right of the green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of bread on the counter next to the sponge.

high_descs: Go to the counter left of the stove
Pick up a knife from the counter
Go to the counter left of the fridge
Cut the loaf of bread
Place the knife on the counter
Take a slice of bread
Go to the microwave
Heat the slice of bread in the microwave
Go to the counter left of the stove
Place the slice of bread on the counter
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of bread on a countertop
